verbose_text: Similar changes in long-chain acylcarnitines were seen in flies with mildly reduced ATPsyndelta expression driven by attenuated expression of ATPsyndelta RNAi (C12 and C14 :1), wheras alterations in cardiolipin (CL) profile lipids, highly enriched in mitochondrial inner membranes, XREF_BIBR (XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY B and XREF_SUPPLEMENTARY) were uniquely observed in fly homogenates.
